data.description: Beautiful four year old single story home with no HOA. The layout of the house connects the living room, dining room & kitchen creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings. Nice looking kitchen with granite counter tops & back splash. Tile flooring throughout the home with no carpet. Brick front on home with stucco on the sides and back. Nice size backyard. This house is conveniently located near schools, shopping centers and only minutes away from Randolph Air Force Base. Easy access to main highways such as I-10 and I-35.
